      <title>欧洲央行的 Scicluna 告诉 Econostream 4 月份可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ecb-s-scicluna-tells-econostream-april-rate-cut-is-possible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员爱德华·希克鲁纳 (Edward Scicluna) 向 Econostream Media 表示，欧洲央行最早可能在 4 月份降息，且不排除这种可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ecb-s-scicluna-tells-econostream-april-rate-cut-is-possible</guid>
