      <title>Meloni 官员预计意大利将克服悲观预测，实现 1% 的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/meloni-officials-see-italy-defying-gloomy-forecasts-to-grow-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 的官员认为，意大利经济今年将增长 1% 左右，超出悲观预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/meloni-officials-see-italy-defying-gloomy-forecasts-to-grow-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
